    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>It does not exactly answer your question, but to get around the problem, </p>\n\n<ol>\n<li><p>you can either create a .cmd file with following content:</p>\n\n<p><code>start netbeans --jdkhome c:\\path\\to\\jdk</code></p></li>\n<li><p>or in the shortcut of Netbeans set the above option.</p></li>\n</ol>\n"
